critical_issues.title: Zero Engagement with Content and Campaigns
critical_issues.description: All the content and campaigns have zero engagement. This indicates either a problem with the content/campaigns themselves, or with the tracking system.
critical_issues.action_required: Investigate and resolve the issues with the tracking system. If the system is working correctly, review the content and campaigns for quality and relevance.

critical_issues.title: No Sales Despite Product Availability
critical_issues.description: There are 81 products available, but no sales. This indicates a problem with the product visibility, pricing, or marketing strategy.
critical_issues.action_required: Review the product visibility on the platform, pricing strategy, and marketing efforts. Consider running promotions or discounts to attract customers.

missed_opportunities.title: Lack of Diversified Revenue Streams
missed_opportunities.description: The business is solely relying on direct sales, with no other revenue streams.
missed_opportunities.action_required: Explore other revenue streams such as affiliate marketing, partnerships, or subscriptions.

blind_spots.title: Low Lead Conversion
blind_spots.description: There is only one lead, and it did not convert. This indicates a problem with the lead generation or conversion strategy.
blind_spots.action_required: Review the lead generation strategy and improve the conversion process. Consider offering incentives or personalized follow-ups.

quick_wins.title: Optimize Content and Campaigns
quick_wins.description: The current content and campaigns are not engaging. Improving them could lead to quick wins.
quick_wins.action_required: Review the content and campaigns, and make them more engaging and relevant. Use data to understand what resonates with the audience.

strategic_risks.title: Reliance on a Single Revenue Generation System
strategic_risks.description: The business is heavily reliant on a single revenue generation system. If it fails, the business could suffer significant losses.
strategic_risks.action_required: Diversify the revenue generation systems to reduce risk.

long_term_strategy.title: Invest in Data Analytics
long_term_strategy.description: The business lacks a data-driven approach to understand what works and what doesn't. Investing in data analytics could provide valuable insights.
long_term_strategy.action_required: Invest in a data analytics tool or hire a data analyst. Use the insights to improve the business strategy.
